666
00:27:11,520 --> 00:27:14,080
What kind of life was that?

667
00:27:14,080 --> 00:27:17,400
話佢係一個照命人生四十年嘅居留

668
00:27:17,400 --> 00:27:19,960
If you call it a calling driven life

669
00:27:19,960 --> 00:27:21,120
Please raise your hand

670
